      <title>大众汽车销量因中国市场及美国、欧洲电动汽车需求下滑而下滑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-11/porsche-s-china-sales-plunge-as-electric-taycan-falls-flat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于向电动汽车转型的进程中举步维艰，大众汽车集团第三季度全球销量下降 7%，其中亚洲和欧洲销量下滑最为严重。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-11/porsche-s-china-sales-plunge-as-electric-taycan-falls-flat</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 11 Oct 2024 07:00:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
